name: Tezpunks
description:
Tezpunks

Year AD 7702, a group of punks are assigned a mysterious mission. These punks are very deadly. They have their own superpowers. Objectives of the mission will be communicated to them from the command center. For now, the only objective communicated to the punks is to time travel to 2021. 

ID #009
Female


Name         : Memtainne 
Strength     : 81/100
Intelligence : 86/100


Memtainne was deported from her planet and spent years in the Kupparnaf mountains acquiring knowledge from the five sages and helping them in black magic. 
The most beautiful and one of the most deadliest punks sent to earth.
